{"tid":389890,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"請教增磅奶粉","createTime":"2017-09-06T15:35:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T22:48:49.000Z","uid":30495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7ab5f1de7bbb130bf1d602d4bfe91976515a4112","tid":389890,"uid":30495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:35:38.000Z","msg":"首先 我係瘦底 166cm 得50kg左右<br />\n我一直有做開運動 本身53kg左右<br />\n自從上年腳整親十字韌帶做手術<br />\n瘦咗好多跌到47kg<br />\n依家一直食野都只係50kg<br />\n以前有做開運動都有肌肉 依家排骨仔<br />\n<br />\n我想買增磅奶粉 有咩好介紹 我會日日操返佢<br />\n但我唔清楚邊個啱我 怕人地介紹錯亂買<br />\n<br />\n請問有無巴打食開可以介紹下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c1ecc949a4ef1ac8f052c84bd053efe81af9574","tid":389890,"uid":70988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:37:13.000Z","msg":"咁瘦?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食多d野先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb18affd356d0655016e2d8cb4c764a0f659b55d","tid":389890,"uid":143774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:44:17.000Z","msg":"其實唔一定要食增磅，可以食多幾餐仲好，因為增磅粉好撚多糖去谷個卡路里，你食乳清蛋白再食多幾餐對身體仲更加好<br />\n仲有增磅粉我覺得幾難入口，無論朱古力又好，雲尼拿又好，個感覺好痴口，好似飲膠水咁，粉又難溶，一舊舊咁<br />\n已經無下次"},{"pid":"76e063e3b35f9309c3b6da65f9f8b9a96e095c64","tid":389890,"uid":30495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:48:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁瘦?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食多d野先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我做地盤嘅 早 午 下午 晚 都有 兩碗飯夠唔夠多"},{"pid":"2a49d3cfd84f2bd830330b4848e9f5aada6da7f4","tid":389890,"uid":30495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:48:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實唔一定要食增磅，可以食多幾餐仲好，因為增磅